title: Analyzing the Impact of Housing Supply & Prices on Homelessness.
description: Developing a simulation model to analyze impact of housing supply and price fluctuation on homelessness in collaboration with Data Science Alliance. Responsibilities: Data collection, preprocessing, feature engineering, model evaluation and performance tuning.

title: Saturated Fat Analysis in Recipes
description: Analyzed food.com dataset in collaboration with friend for DSC 80 final project. Built regression model with StandardScaler and GradientBoostingRegressor. Used RandomizedSearchCV for hyperparameter tuning.

title: Deriving Value from Transaction Data
description: Worked with 3 peers under guidance of Deloitte consultant to perform extensive analysis of e-commerce dataset of over 90,000 records. Translated patterns & model predictions into actionable insights & business strategy recommendations. Presented findings to Deloitte and Halicioglu Data Science Institute experts through engaging data visualization.

title: Africa Economic Crisis Analysis
description: Analyzed economic and banking data from 13 African countries. Used Tableau to visualize trends & performed background research to gain context for patterns and outliers observed.

title: Geospatial Visualization of Boston Bike Stations
description: Utilized D3.js, HTML and CSS to build an interactive geospatial visualization that portays bike lanes, stations and traffic in Boston and Cambridge.
